SWINE FEVER/HOG CHOLERA - BELGIUM
*********************************
Date: Wed, 02 Jul 1997 23:53:58 -0400
From: Robert A. LaBudde <ral@lcfltd.com>
[see
Swine fever/Hog cholera - Spain 970426150528
